29#ifndef _ZFEATURE_COMMON_H
30#define _ZFEATURE_COMMON_H
31
32#include <sys/fs/zfs.h>
33#include <sys/types.h>
34
35#ifdef __cplusplus
36extern "C" {
37#endif
38
39struct zfeature_info;
40
41typedef enum spa_feature {
42 SPA_FEATURE_NONE = -1,
43 SPA_FEATURE_ASYNC_DESTROY,
44 SPA_FEATURE_EMPTY_BPOBJ,
45 SPA_FEATURE_LZ4_COMPRESS,
46 SPA_FEATURE_MULTI_VDEV_CRASH_DUMP,
47 SPA_FEATURE_SPACEMAP_HISTOGRAM,
48 SPA_FEATURE_ENABLED_TXG,
49 SPA_FEATURE_HOLE_BIRTH,
50 SPA_FEATURE_EXTENSIBLE_DATASET,
51 SPA_FEATURE_EMBEDDED_DATA,
52 SPA_FEATURE_BOOKMARKS,
53 SPA_FEATURE_FS_SS_LIMIT,
54 SPA_FEATURE_LARGE_BLOCKS,
55#ifndef __NetBSD__
56 SPA_FEATURE_SHA512,
57 SPA_FEATURE_SKEIN,
58#endif
59#ifdef illumos
60 SPA_FEATURE_EDONR,
61#endif
62 SPA_FEATURES
63} spa_feature_t;
64
65#define SPA_FEATURE_DISABLED (-1ULL)
66
67typedef enum zfeature_flags {
68 /* Can open pool readonly even if this feature is not supported. */
69 ZFEATURE_FLAG_READONLY_COMPAT = (1 << 0),
70 /* Is this feature necessary to read the MOS? */
71 ZFEATURE_FLAG_MOS = (1 << 1),
72 /* Activate this feature at the same time it is enabled. */
73 ZFEATURE_FLAG_ACTIVATE_ON_ENABLE = (1 << 2),
74 /* Each dataset has a field set if it has ever used this feature. */
75 ZFEATURE_FLAG_PER_DATASET = (1 << 3)
76} zfeature_flags_t;
77
78typedef struct zfeature_info {
79 spa_feature_t fi_feature;
80 const char *fi_uname; /* User-facing feature name */
81 const char *fi_guid; /* On-disk feature identifier */
82 const char *fi_desc; /* Feature description */
83 zfeature_flags_t fi_flags;
84 /* array of dependencies, terminated by SPA_FEATURE_NONE */
85 const spa_feature_t *fi_depends;
86} zfeature_info_t;
87
88typedef int (zfeature_func_t)(zfeature_info_t *, void *);
89
90#define ZFS_FEATURE_DEBUG
91
92extern zfeature_info_t spa_feature_table[SPA_FEATURES];
93
94extern boolean_t zfeature_is_valid_guid(const char *);
95
96extern boolean_t zfeature_is_supported(const char *);
97extern int zfeature_lookup_name(const char *, spa_feature_t *);
98extern boolean_t zfeature_depends_on(spa_feature_t, spa_feature_t);
99
100extern void zpool_feature_init(void);
101
102#ifdef __cplusplus
103}
104#endif
105
106#endif /* _ZFEATURE_COMMON_H */
107
